Aye muggles aye n-chi anq´in toj Grimmauld Place otaq tzik´x ky-k´amo´n aye b´a´n
nya b´a´n toj tajlal aju tzaj tqona aju tajlal junlaj tu´n tkub´ qe ttxlaj tajlal
oxlaj.
extzen aye plas jalin n-chi tzaj ky-txko´n junjun xjal n-chi pon ky-ka´yin aye n-chi b´et ky-b´i´n
q´onka twitza ti´j anomalía mas b´a´n. Noq jun q´ij ik´x myia jun moqa kab´e
xjal n-chi pon toj Grimmauld Place mya tuk´e juntl ky-b´inchb´en, moqa ikyx t-xilen,
twitzju tuʼn t-xi qʼet qʼuqbʼil qkʼuʼj tiʼj barandilla in nok qkeʼyin kyiʼj tajlal once ex oxlaj, tuʼn tok qqʼoʼn qwitz tiʼj
aju tmojb´ab´il kyxol kab´e ja. Aye lurkers mya junx kyten kab´e q´ij
n-chi b´et, maske kykyaqil n-chi ky-b´inchen jun nya b´a´n ti´j ky-xb´alun. Nintz
kye aye xjal te Londres n-chi ik´x kyi´j, n-chi b´et ky-b´inchen ky-xb´alun extzen n-chi kyi´n
ch´in t-xilen, maske at maj jun kyxol jaku tz´ok tka´yin t-xe, n-xjel
tiquʼn at jun xjal jaku tzʼok tqʼoʼn jun t-xbʼalun nim twaʼlil toj qʼaqʼ.
Aye xjal n-chi ka´yin ikyjo n-chi tzaj ky-k´amo´n ch´in tzalajb´il ti´j ky-vigilia. At maj jun kyxol n-chi tzyet tu´n t-xi´ twitz tuk´e tzalajb´il, ik tza´n otaq tz´ok tka´yin jun ti´x
b´a´n t-xilen, noq tu´n t-xi´ t-xo´n t-xe t-xilen.
